Cheng Qingcong!

348
00:40:35,200 --> 00:40:38,100
I like you. I'm serious.

349
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:43,400
I know I'm a killjoy and not smart.

350
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:49,600
I can never tell if you're being serious... or just making a joke.

351
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:53,100
So can you think about it carefully before telling me anything next time?

352
00:40:53,100 --> 00:40:54,700
Because I'll take it seriously.

353
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:56,300
I'm not joking.

354
00:40:57,300 --> 00:40:59,700
I swear in the name of Hippocrates.

